        <abstract>
            <p>Paris is in the hands of "brigands and socialists", but one grows accustomed to sporadic bombardment,</p>
            <p>and VOK is peacefully studying invertebrate palaeontology collections.</p> 
<p>Reports on Paul Gervais’ successful cross between a <hi rend="italic">Triton</hi> and an axolotl.</p> 
